import React from 'react'
import { AppBar, Typography, Toolbar, Box, Button } from '@mui/material'

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <AppBar position='sticky' sx={{ background: "linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(57,24,9,1) 0%, rgba(167,124,100,1) 85%)" }}>
            <Toolbar>
                <Typography variant='h4'>Blogg</Typography>
                <Box display="flex" marginLeft="auto">
                    <Button variant='text' sx={{ margin: 1, borderRadius: 2 }} style={{ color: 'white' }}>Login</Button>
                    <Button variant='text' sx={{ margin: 1, borderRadius: 2 }} style={{ color: 'white' }}>Signup</Button>
                </Box>
            </Toolbar>
        </AppBar>
    )
}

export default Header
